org.dspace.importer.external.metadatamapping

Class MetadataFieldConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dspace.importer.external.metadatamapping.MetadataFieldConfig

  • public class MetadataFieldConfig
extends Object
    A generalised configuration for metadatafields. This is used to make the link between values and the actual MetadatumDTO object.
    Author:
    Roeland Dillen (roeland at atmire dot com)
